# Design System Token Rules - Foundation Layer

## 🎯 **Purpose**
This file defines the **semantic design tokens** that should be used across all platforms. 
**For implementation details, see platform-specific rules:**
- **Flutter**: `flutter-ds-rules.mdc`

## 🎨 Color System

### **Primary Color Palette**
    ```
    Ocean Navy:    #003763  (Primary - Base dark)
    Sky Blue:      #61B3E4  (Accent - Primary highlight)
    Coral Orange:  #EF7521  (Motivational accent)
    Sun Gold:      #F6B333  (Secondary accent)
    Ivory White:   #FFFFFF  (Contrast base)
    Seafoam Teal:  #3CA6A6  (Tertiary accent)
    Cream Sand:    #F2E3D5  (Card background)
    ```
### **Primary Color Palette - Darker shade**
    ```
    Ocean Navy:    #12192E  (Primary - Base dark)
    Sky Blue:      #1C668D  (Accent - Primary highlight)
    Coral Orange:  #873C0D  (Motivational accent)
    Sun Gold:      #B1870C  (Secondary accent)
    Ivory White:   #C0C0C0  (Contrast base)
    Seafoam Teal:  #1D5454  (Tertiary accent)
    Cream Sand:    #F2E3D5  (Card background)
    ```

### **Primary Color Palette - Lighter shade**
    ```
    Ocean Navy:    #003763  (Primary - Base dark)
    Sky Blue:      #61B3E4  (Accent - Primary highlight)
    Coral Orange:  #EF7521  (Motivational accent)
    Sun Gold:      #F6B333  (Secondary accent)
    Ivory White:   #FFFFFF  (Contrast base)
    Seafoam Teal:  #4EE2E2  (Tertiary accent)
