## 📏 Spacing System

### **Spacing Scale**
```
xs:    4px   (Extra Small)
sm:    8px   (Small)
md:    12px  (Medium)
lg:    16px  (Large)
xl:    24px  (Extra Large)
xxl:   32px  (2X Large)
xxxl:  48px  (3X Large)
```

## 🎯 Border Radius

### **Radius Scale**
```
sm:    8px   (Small)
md:    12px  (Medium)
lg:    16px  (Large)
xl:    24px  (Extra Large)
```

## 📝 Typography

### **Font Families**
```
Headings: Merriweather (serif)
Body:     Inter (sans-serif)
```

### **Font Scale**
```
xs:    12px  (Extra Small)
sm:    14px  (Small)
md:    16px  (Medium)
lg:    18px  (Large)
xl:    20px  (Extra Large)
xxl:    24px (2X Large)
xxxl:   32px (3X Large)
display: 48px (Display)
```

## 🎨 Elevation & Shadows

### **Elevation Scale**
```
none:  0px   (No elevation)
sm:    1px   (Small)
md:    2px   (Medium)
lg:    4px   (Large)
xl:    8px   (Extra Large)
```

## 🔘 Component Tokens

### **Button Heights**
```
sm:    32px  (Small)
md:    40px  (Medium)
lg:    48px  (Large)
xl:    56px  (Extra Large)
```

### **Input Heights**
```
sm:    32px  (Small)
md:    40px  (Medium)
lg:    48px  (Large)
```

### **Card Padding**
```
sm:    12px  (Small)
md:    16px  (Medium)
lg:    24px  (Large)
xl:    32px  (Extra Large)
```

## 🎯 Breakpoints

### **Responsive Breakpoints**
```
mobile:    320px   (Mobile devices)
tablet:    768px   (Tablet devices)
desktop:   1024px  (Desktop devices)
wide:      1440px  (Wide screens)
```

## 🎨 Animation Tokens

### **Duration Scale**
```
fast:   150ms  (Fast animations)
normal: 300ms  (Normal animations)
slow:   500ms  (Slow animations)
```

### **Easing Functions**
```
ease-in:     cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 1, 1)
ease-out:    cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1)
ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)
```

## 🎯 Icon Sizes

### **Icon Scale**
```
sm:    16px  (Small)
md:    24px  (Medium)
lg:    32px  (Large)
xl:    48px  (Extra Large)
xxl:    64px (2X Large)
```

## 🎨 Z-Index Scale

### **Z-Index Tokens**
```
base:     0    (Base layer)
card:     1    (Card layer)
dropdown: 10   (Dropdown layer)
modal:    100  (Modal layer)
tooltip:  200  (Tooltip layer)
toast:    300  (Toast layer)
```

## 🎯 Semantic Naming Convention

### **Token Categories**
```
{category}-{property}-{size}
Examples:
- color-primary
- spacing-lg
- typography-heading-xl
- radius-md
- elevation-lg
```

